title: Ep - 128 - TYLER CRISPEN FROM BIG BROTHER, LIZ WOODBURN FROM MADE IN MEXICO, NIKKI GLASER FROM DANCING WITH THE STARS
description:
Tyler Crispen from Big Brother season 20 talks about finding love with Angela, his game strategy, and behind the scenes of the show. 


Liz Woodburn from Netflix’ first-ever Mexican reality series, Made In Mexico, talks about joining the cast and life in Mexico City. The Spanish-language series follows nine wealthy socialites as they navigate wealth, friendships, and romance. 


Comedian Nikki Glaser talks about being cast on this season of Dancing With the Stars, whether she will miss wearing sequins, and if it is torture wearing open toe boots when salsa dancing.
